@model WebApplication2.Models.newAnamnesis
@using WebApplication2.Models
@using (Html.BeginForm("Create", "Anamnesis", FormMethod.Post,  new { id = "AnamnesisCreate" }))
{
    @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
    @Html.HiddenFor(model=>model.visitID)
    @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.num)

    <div class="form-horizontal">

        @Html.ValidationSummary(true, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })


        <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                @Html.DropDownListFor(model=>model.anamnesis.type.ID, new SelectList(Model.eventTypes, "ID", "name"), new { @class = "form-control"  })
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.anamnesis.type.ID, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                @Html.EditorFor(model => model.anamnesis.comments, new { htmlAttributes = new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.anamnesis.comments) } })
                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.anamnesis.comments, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2">
                
                <a onclick="PostCreateForm('Anamnesis', @Model.num)" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
}